\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {12}{\ignorespaces Actual versus predicted close price for ModernTCN\xspace  on BTC/USDT, $h = 4$ (seed~123). (a)~At step~1, the model tracks the actual price with high fidelity, capturing directional turns and amplitude fluctuations. (b)~At step~4, trend structure is preserved but short-lived volatility spikes are modestly attenuated, consistent with MSE-induced shrinkage. No systematic phase shift is observed.}}{36}{figure.caption.40}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:pred_btc_h4_step1_step4}{{12}{36}{Actual versus predicted close price for \moderntcn on BTC/USDT, $h = 4$ (seed~123). (a)~At step~1, the model tracks the actual price with high fidelity, capturing directional turns and amplitude fluctuations. (b)~At step~4, trend structure is preserved but short-lived volatility spikes are modestly attenuated, consistent with MSE-induced shrinkage. No systematic phase shift is observed}{figure.caption.40}{}}
